WEBVTT

00:00:02.043 --> 00:00:04.754
WRITTEN BY HYUGA NATSU

00:01:31.508 --> 00:01:32.926
{\an8}THIS STORY IS A FICTION AND ALL NAMES OF
FIGURES AND ORGANIZATIONS ARE FICTITIOUS.

00:01:33.009 --> 00:01:34.385
{\an8}MOREOVER, THE STORY HAS NO RELATION
TO REAL-LIFE INCIDENTS AND EVENTS.

00:01:36.054 --> 00:01:38.223
<i>That whistle! Must be Lihaku.</i>

00:01:38.807 --> 00:01:41.184
<i>So he got Maomao out of the fortress.</i>

00:01:42.101 --> 00:01:43.436
Basen,

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:45.146
take it easy.

00:01:45.230 --> 00:01:47.357
Then let me go ahead first!

00:01:53.655 --> 00:01:54.948
Wait, step back.

00:01:55.698 --> 00:01:57.575
- Feifa!
- Let’s go!

00:01:57.659 --> 00:01:58.701
Damn it!

00:02:03.623 --> 00:02:05.041
Where is Shishou?

00:02:05.125 --> 00:02:08.962
I don’t know! We were tricked, that’s all!

00:02:09.045 --> 00:02:11.214
Bold of you to say!

00:02:11.297 --> 00:02:14.843
Evidence shows you embezzled national
funds, using them to build this fortress!

00:02:15.718 --> 00:02:17.637
You know what that means!

00:02:18.138 --> 00:02:20.265
We were told, it was for the country!

00:02:20.348 --> 00:02:23.309
We thought it was all for the nation!

00:02:24.769 --> 00:02:27.063
How merciful of you.

00:02:31.359 --> 00:02:33.778
If he is going to be executed anyway,

00:02:34.863 --> 00:02:38.116
- you may as well finish him off cleanly.
- Shishou!

00:02:39.951 --> 00:02:43.621
How relaxed you sound, Shishou.

00:02:45.206 --> 00:02:46.374
{\an8}By imperial decree,

00:02:47.041 --> 00:02:49.836
you are under arrest
for embezzlement and treason.

00:02:49.919 --> 00:02:55.174
The Forbidden Army is here.
I assumed an edict had been issued.

00:02:55.258 --> 00:02:57.635
Senile, are you?
You do not even have a spark.

00:02:59.178 --> 00:03:00.054
Down!

00:03:04.726 --> 00:03:06.853
How pitiful.

00:03:06.936 --> 00:03:11.065
You used to shoot animals for sport,
itching to try it on a person someday.

00:03:11.149 --> 00:03:15.028
What a pity you never got the chance.

00:03:15.111 --> 00:03:16.195
How disappointing.

00:03:16.279 --> 00:03:17.864
I never said that!

00:03:17.947 --> 00:03:19.657
There's no spark.

00:03:19.741 --> 00:03:23.328
It is a new model.
It can fire without a spark.

00:03:23.411 --> 00:03:25.663
Ah, so you were aware.

00:03:25.747 --> 00:03:27.749
I was attacked with one, after all.

00:03:28.333 --> 00:03:30.585
A pity.

00:03:30.668 --> 00:03:32.545
Had I succeeded then.

00:03:33.588 --> 00:03:35.548
Such a waste.

00:03:37.175 --> 00:03:38.426
So this is it.

00:03:39.219 --> 00:03:41.429
If I had more time.

00:03:42.013 --> 00:03:45.099
No, perhaps nothing would
change regardless.

00:03:45.725 --> 00:03:46.726
<i>What is this?</i>

00:03:47.310 --> 00:03:49.896
<i>He sounds like he is reading
from a prepared script.</i>

00:03:52.649 --> 00:03:53.900
Move in!

00:04:29.686 --> 00:04:34.023
<i>It feels like watching a play
about this man named Shishou.</i>

00:04:37.610 --> 00:04:41.990
<i>A favored retainer since the previous
emperor’s reign, now a traitor.</i>

00:04:42.073 --> 00:04:43.783
<i>It’s anticlimactic, to say the least.</i>

00:04:44.826 --> 00:04:46.494
<i>Such was his end.</i>

00:04:48.371 --> 00:04:50.290
{\an8}We have not done anything!

00:04:50.373 --> 00:04:52.917
{\an8}Lady Shenmei and Loulan
are in the back room!

00:04:53.751 --> 00:04:55.712
- I am leaving this to you.
- Yes, Sir!

00:05:01.551 --> 00:05:03.386
- I leave the other side to you.
- Understood.

00:05:17.650 --> 00:05:19.068
Boom!

00:05:20.695 --> 00:05:21.946
Loulan.

00:05:22.030 --> 00:05:24.365
Greetings, Moon Prince.

00:05:24.866 --> 00:05:28.828
{\an8}No, for convenience,
I shall call you Lord Jinshi.

00:05:30.246 --> 00:05:32.999
Would you be so kind as to follow me?

00:05:33.082 --> 00:05:34.334
And if I refuse?

00:05:34.417 --> 00:05:37.295
That is precisely why I am
threatening you.

00:05:39.213 --> 00:05:41.924
How obedient of you
to come along so willingly.

00:05:42.633 --> 00:05:45.219
You were the one
who told me to follow you.

00:05:45.887 --> 00:05:50.349
But surely, taking this from me
would not be difficult for you?

00:05:54.395 --> 00:05:55.229
This way.

00:05:57.565 --> 00:06:01.235
Sister Suirei,
are they not hurting you anymore?

00:06:02.403 --> 00:06:03.780
<i>So this is Suirei.</i>

00:06:04.655 --> 00:06:08.576
<i>She coaxed the court physician,
faked her death, escaped,</i>

00:06:08.659 --> 00:06:11.579
<i>and returned disguised as a eunuch.</i>

00:06:12.622 --> 00:06:14.874
<i>I always thought her bold.</i>

00:06:16.167 --> 00:06:18.544
Loulan, no. That man is.

00:06:18.628 --> 00:06:22.548
I brought him to fulfil your wish, Mother.

00:06:24.509 --> 00:06:26.677
You have always hated the one

00:06:26.761 --> 00:06:29.013
who resembled this figure, haven’t you?

00:06:29.597 --> 00:06:32.975
Was it jealousy because she was
far more beautiful than you?

00:06:33.768 --> 00:06:38.064
Or was it because he chose an attendant
who was far younger than you?

00:06:39.065 --> 00:06:41.984
Even though you were a senior consort,
he never visited your bedroom.

00:06:42.068 --> 00:06:43.903
{\an8}Loulan!!!

00:06:44.529 --> 00:06:46.781
Forgive me. That may have gone too far.

00:06:47.573 --> 00:06:51.119
Now then,
before you fulfil your final desire,

00:06:51.202 --> 00:06:53.287
shall we have a little show first??

00:06:55.873 --> 00:06:58.918
This happened more than 30 years ago.

00:06:59.001 --> 00:07:02.713
The late emperor was a dim-witted man,
unable to defy his mother.

00:07:03.381 --> 00:07:07.260
<i>As a result, she wielded true power</i>

00:07:07.343 --> 00:07:09.720
<i>and was called the Empress in the Shadows.</i>

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:14.725
<i>Tired of her son’s lack of interest
in women,</i>

00:07:15.309 --> 00:07:18.438
<i>she kept sending beautiful women
into the rear palace.</i>

00:07:19.605 --> 00:07:20.898
<i>And then, one day.</i>

00:07:21.732 --> 00:07:22.775
Shenmei,

00:07:23.484 --> 00:07:26.904
is it true you are entering
the rear palace?

00:07:26.988 --> 00:07:29.991
Yes, as a senior-ranking consort,
by request.

00:07:30.074 --> 00:07:32.994
But you were to be, with me.

00:07:33.077 --> 00:07:35.246
That plan is cancelled.

00:07:36.205 --> 00:07:38.916
Do you not understand? This is my chance.

00:07:39.959 --> 00:07:43.504
If I bear the emperor’s child,
the seat of empress could be mine.

00:07:44.005 --> 00:07:46.841
I will not settle for being the wife

00:07:46.924 --> 00:07:48.509
of a northern lord!

00:07:49.969 --> 00:07:51.387
Shenmei.

00:07:51.471 --> 00:07:54.640
She was chosen as
the emperor’s senior-ranking consort.

00:07:54.724 --> 00:07:57.518
But that was merely the official story.

00:07:57.602 --> 00:08:01.230
Official story?
What are you talking about, Loulan?

00:08:01.314 --> 00:08:03.316
I was brought in
as a senior consort by request.

00:08:04.650 --> 00:08:07.653
That was your assumption.

00:08:07.737 --> 00:08:10.406
I heard it from Grandfather
as he lay on his sickbed.

00:08:10.490 --> 00:08:13.117
He kept muttering like a curse,

00:08:13.201 --> 00:08:16.871
"With my daughter held hostage,
I could do nothing."

00:08:16.954 --> 00:08:18.372
Hostage?

00:08:18.456 --> 00:08:23.252
A high official's daughter may be called
a "consort" and taken as a hostage.

00:08:25.671 --> 00:08:29.342
Father once gave up on you,

00:08:29.425 --> 00:08:32.803
but then something unexpected happened.

00:08:32.887 --> 00:08:35.139
The late emperor’s proclivities.

00:08:35.223 --> 00:08:40.102
Lord Jinshi, do you know
why the rear palace became so large?

00:08:40.186 --> 00:08:43.481
I heard Shishou encouraged
the Empress in the Shadows.

00:08:43.564 --> 00:08:46.817
Yes, he proposed expanding the palace

00:08:46.901 --> 00:08:50.029
as a new public project.

00:08:50.112 --> 00:08:51.822
A replacement for the slave trade.

00:08:52.823 --> 00:08:54.283
Slave trade?

00:08:55.618 --> 00:08:59.372
It seems you truly know nothing, Mother.

00:08:59.455 --> 00:09:03.167
Do you even know what Grandfather did
to draw the empress’s attention?

00:09:03.251 --> 00:09:06.003
But back then, slavery was still legal.

00:09:06.963 --> 00:09:10.091
<i>I heard they were treated similarly
to courtesans in the pleasure district.</i>

00:09:10.174 --> 00:09:14.804
<i>But those sold to foreign lands
were different.</i>

00:09:15.388 --> 00:09:19.725
That is why the empress
outlawed the slave trade.

00:09:19.809 --> 00:09:22.728
The Shi family,
whose trade had long been in slaves,

00:09:22.812 --> 00:09:26.774
had no choice but to scale it back after
their daughters were taken as hostages.

00:09:27.400 --> 00:09:30.361
At that time, with no options left,

00:09:30.444 --> 00:09:32.697
Father made a proposal to Grandfather.

00:09:33.531 --> 00:09:35.866
What if we use the rear palace

00:09:35.950 --> 00:09:37.743
as a destination for the remaining slaves?

00:09:38.703 --> 00:09:41.372
Young girls can become maids
or palace women,

00:09:41.455 --> 00:09:44.250
and the boys, eunuchs.

00:09:44.333 --> 00:09:48.921
If we say it is for the emperor,
who has no interest in women,

00:09:49.005 --> 00:09:50.506
the empress may accept it.

00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:53.509
Indeed, families who sold their daughters

00:09:53.593 --> 00:09:55.052
may feel less guilt

00:09:55.136 --> 00:09:58.723
if they enter the rear palace
rather than being sold abroad.

00:09:58.806 --> 00:09:59.807
Exactly.

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:03.644
{\an8}It benefits everyone.

00:10:03.728 --> 00:10:07.148
By earning the empress’s trust,
Father hoped to restore

00:10:07.231 --> 00:10:09.317
the Shi clan’s honor,

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:12.778
and to reclaim you, Mother,
held as a hostage.

00:10:12.862 --> 00:10:14.780
It must have been hard for you.

00:10:15.990 --> 00:10:17.158
Running away earlier

00:10:18.284 --> 00:10:20.494
would have been wiser now.

00:10:26.208 --> 00:10:28.669
Shishou? How did you?

00:10:28.753 --> 00:10:31.714
I made a secret passage. Shenmei,

00:10:32.506 --> 00:10:34.050
will you not come with me?

00:10:35.426 --> 00:10:38.262
{\an8}If you wish it, let us escape together.

00:10:38.346 --> 00:10:41.599
Escaping from the rear palace
is a capital offense.

00:10:41.682 --> 00:10:44.143
Making a secret passage
is already treason.

00:10:44.727 --> 00:10:47.730
I could never give you up.

00:10:47.813 --> 00:10:50.691
I could not marry anyone else,
and I came this far

00:10:50.775 --> 00:10:52.526
because I wanted to see you again.

00:10:54.945 --> 00:10:57.907
- Are you sure you want me?
- Of course I do.

00:10:59.992 --> 00:11:01.118
Now come.

00:11:09.460 --> 00:11:13.714
Is that the high-ranking consort
who got upstaged by the attendant Taihou?

00:11:13.798 --> 00:11:17.218
Even though she entered before Lady Anshi.

00:11:17.301 --> 00:11:20.346
I hear the emperor has never
visited her chambers, not even once.

00:11:21.472 --> 00:11:22.765
Do not make a fool of me!

00:11:22.848 --> 00:11:25.976
You would have me escape
with that shame lingering on me?

00:11:26.060 --> 00:11:26.936
That is not it!

00:11:27.019 --> 00:11:27.937
Get out!

00:11:30.815 --> 00:11:34.151
<i>Was it that you could not trust a man
willing to throw away</i>

00:11:34.235 --> 00:11:36.237
his own status for you?

00:11:36.821 --> 00:11:40.324
There is no way
I could trust a man like that!

00:11:40.408 --> 00:11:42.868
Right after my father collapsed,

00:11:42.952 --> 00:11:46.205
he took over the clan
and then married this woman’s mother!

00:11:50.042 --> 00:11:51.085
Sister,

00:11:51.168 --> 00:11:52.795
forgive me please.

00:11:57.716 --> 00:12:01.011
That is the phoenix hairpin!

00:12:01.095 --> 00:12:04.473
Yes. As you well know,

00:12:04.557 --> 00:12:06.684
this ornament,

00:12:06.767 --> 00:12:08.352
<i>like the qilin design,</i>

00:12:08.436 --> 00:12:10.688
<i>is only worn by those of imperial blood.</i>

00:12:10.771 --> 00:12:14.775
Lies!
The late emperor never acknowledged her!

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:19.113
It seems he carried guilt.

00:12:19.697 --> 00:12:23.200
He worried about the baby
he cast out of the rear palace.

00:12:23.284 --> 00:12:26.787
From time to time, he would visit,
aided by Father.

00:12:28.247 --> 00:12:30.249
He once denied it,

00:12:30.332 --> 00:12:32.918
but eventually recognized her
as his daughter.

00:12:33.002 --> 00:12:35.296
And so, he made a request of Father.

00:12:36.172 --> 00:12:39.383
I want you to take my daughter
as your wife.

00:12:40.134 --> 00:12:44.597
<i>Father accepted the child born between
attendant Taihou and the late emperor</i>

00:12:44.680 --> 00:12:46.140
<i>as his wife.</i>

00:12:47.224 --> 00:12:50.311
<i>And eventually,
they had a child of their own.</i>

00:12:51.604 --> 00:12:53.439
We have named her Shisui.

00:12:53.522 --> 00:12:58.027
Shisui, a fine name
for one of the Shi clan.

00:12:58.110 --> 00:13:01.947
Lord, you said you would grant
any wish of mine.

00:13:02.031 --> 00:13:05.784
Then please,
grant me Senior Consort Shenmei

00:13:05.868 --> 00:13:07.953
as a reward.

00:13:08.037 --> 00:13:10.122
When the late emperor saw his grandchild

00:13:10.206 --> 00:13:12.458
bearing the "Shi" name, he was satisfied.

00:13:12.541 --> 00:13:15.127
There was no longer
any need for a hostage.

00:13:15.753 --> 00:13:18.839
And so, Mother, you were given to Father.

00:13:22.343 --> 00:13:25.179
<i>The late emperor was a foolish man.</i>

00:13:25.262 --> 00:13:26.972
<i>He never realized how selfish his wish was</i>

00:13:27.056 --> 00:13:31.769
<i>and how deeply it would affect
the lives of Shishou and his daughter.</i>

00:13:32.353 --> 00:13:33.479
Lies!

00:13:33.562 --> 00:13:35.981
All lies! Don't talk nonsense!

00:13:36.565 --> 00:13:38.192
{\an8}Nonsense, is it?

00:13:38.275 --> 00:13:41.946
{\an8}Even though Father did it all for you?

00:13:42.029 --> 00:13:45.157
{\an8}Knowing there was no salvation
at the end of it?

00:13:49.161 --> 00:13:52.331
Do you not even understand
why Lord Jinshi is here?

00:13:53.874 --> 00:13:56.085
How did Father meet his end?

00:13:57.586 --> 00:13:59.296
<i>He laughed as he said his final words.</i>

00:14:00.422 --> 00:14:03.551
That man only ever wanted power!

00:14:03.634 --> 00:14:07.471
He married me
just to show off his new position!

00:14:08.305 --> 00:14:13.435
And yet, it was you who wielded more
influence than he did within the clan.

00:14:14.061 --> 00:14:19.066
Do you know what your flatterers

00:14:19.149 --> 00:14:20.317
were doing at court?

00:14:20.401 --> 00:14:23.612
You mean the embezzlement
from the treasury?

00:14:23.696 --> 00:14:27.533
Yes. They took bribes,
stole from the national coffers,

00:14:27.616 --> 00:14:30.494
<i>and anyone who dared speak out
was removed.</i>

00:14:30.578 --> 00:14:32.121
<i>All that remained was rot.</i>

00:14:32.872 --> 00:14:36.000
<i>Father took it all upon himself,
acting as the traitor</i>

00:14:36.083 --> 00:14:39.879
<i>to bring down the rot in the Shi clan.</i>

00:14:40.671 --> 00:14:44.717
Lord Jinshi, they called Father a <i>tanuki,</i>

00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:47.887
but <i>tanuki</i> are timid creatures.

00:14:47.970 --> 00:14:51.682
It is precisely because they are timid
that they try so hard to outsmart others.

00:14:52.433 --> 00:14:54.435
<i>If that story is true,</i>

00:14:54.518 --> 00:14:58.439
<i>rear palace expansion and embezzlement
should be judged separately.</i>

00:14:58.981 --> 00:15:03.736
<i>Shishou played the villain, gathering
the nation’s corruption onto himself.</i>

00:15:04.486 --> 00:15:05.696
<i>What a thankless role.</i>

00:15:05.779 --> 00:15:07.948
Did he play the villain

00:15:08.032 --> 00:15:10.075
well enough?

00:15:11.535 --> 00:15:14.288
And do you have proof this is the truth?

00:15:14.371 --> 00:15:18.959
Thanks to this, much of the rot
in the palace has been cleaned out.

00:15:19.043 --> 00:15:21.420
And what if it had not worked?

00:15:21.503 --> 00:15:25.507
Then we would have simply taken
the country as our own.

00:15:25.591 --> 00:15:28.510
If the nation collapses
from this fragility, let it be gone.

00:15:28.594 --> 00:15:30.721
So you were always with him,

00:15:30.804 --> 00:15:32.473
lying to me?

00:15:32.556 --> 00:15:36.477
I only did what you always said, Mother.

00:15:36.560 --> 00:15:40.439
You wanted the country to fall,
did you not?

00:15:42.524 --> 00:15:46.904
Surrounded with fools who only told you
what you wanted to hear,

00:15:46.987 --> 00:15:49.156
did you believe you could
defeat the Forbidden Army?

00:15:49.239 --> 00:15:50.658
Loulan!!!

00:15:54.244 --> 00:15:57.414
Is that not why you had this made?

00:15:57.498 --> 00:16:00.876
It is too much for you to handle.
Give it to me.

00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:02.795
Shut up!

00:16:03.921 --> 00:16:05.047
What is so funny?

00:16:05.673 --> 00:16:07.883
{\an8}It is just...

00:16:07.967 --> 00:16:10.010
You really are such a small, petty woman.

00:16:10.094 --> 00:16:11.845
Loulan!!

00:16:16.100 --> 00:16:17.476
A gunshot?

00:16:17.559 --> 00:16:18.644
Lord Basen!

00:16:24.358 --> 00:16:26.735
I am a terrible daughter, am I not?

00:16:27.403 --> 00:16:31.490
If I had truly understood my father's
intentions, I wouldn't do this.

00:16:31.573 --> 00:16:34.076
Did you stuff something inside the barrel?

00:16:34.910 --> 00:16:37.621
The newer models are
more complex in design.

00:16:38.122 --> 00:16:42.126
Lord Jinshi, did you never consider
taking it from me then?

00:16:42.209 --> 00:16:45.254
You had plenty of chances.

00:16:45.337 --> 00:16:47.047
You wanted to convey something, right?

00:16:49.049 --> 00:16:51.802
If only you had been
just another pretty fool.

00:16:57.725 --> 00:17:01.311
Mother. Father has died.

00:17:01.395 --> 00:17:03.731
The least you could do is shed a tear.

00:17:04.565 --> 00:17:07.359
He waited for you all this time.

00:17:08.277 --> 00:17:09.945
If you had just shed a single tear,

00:17:10.029 --> 00:17:12.322
even I might not have done
something like this.

00:17:14.533 --> 00:17:17.036
Was there truly no other way?

00:17:17.786 --> 00:17:19.329
Perhaps there was.

00:17:19.997 --> 00:17:22.958
But we were never that clever.

00:17:23.625 --> 00:17:28.505
<i>Shenmei wanted to destroy the country
that scorned her.</i>

00:17:28.589 --> 00:17:32.051
<i>Shishou did everything for her, and yet,</i>

00:17:32.134 --> 00:17:35.804
<i>he was still a loyal subject
who could not turn his back on the nation.</i>

00:17:35.888 --> 00:17:37.222
Lord Jinshi,

00:17:37.931 --> 00:17:39.933
this may sound selfish, but,

00:17:40.017 --> 00:17:42.603
may I ask two things of you?

00:17:44.021 --> 00:17:44.855
What are they?

00:17:45.439 --> 00:17:47.024
Thank you.

00:17:50.027 --> 00:17:51.779
Then, take this.

00:17:56.450 --> 00:18:00.287
To be honest, I meant to use it
as a bargaining chip to beg for my life,

00:18:00.370 --> 00:18:02.247
but it did not go as planned.

00:18:02.998 --> 00:18:04.583
What is written there,

00:18:04.666 --> 00:18:07.586
are the things
that may soon befall this nation.

00:18:09.338 --> 00:18:11.381
This is my first request.

00:18:11.465 --> 00:18:13.717
Those among our clan
who still think clearly

00:18:13.801 --> 00:18:16.095
were exiled by Mother
and have discarded the Shi name.

00:18:16.762 --> 00:18:18.931
My sister is one such person.

00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:22.726
Please, consider them already dead,

00:18:22.810 --> 00:18:24.895
and spare them.

00:18:25.395 --> 00:18:26.522
I will do what I can.

00:18:26.605 --> 00:18:30.943
Then, you will spare the ones
who are "already dead."

00:18:31.527 --> 00:18:33.278
Thank you.

00:18:33.362 --> 00:18:34.530
And the second?

00:18:45.332 --> 00:18:47.417
Now for the second request.

00:19:03.642 --> 00:19:05.185
Thank you.

00:19:05.769 --> 00:19:10.482
Mother, this is all I could do.

00:19:21.493 --> 00:19:24.621
I wonder, could I ever become
a greater actor than Father?

00:21:00.592 --> 00:21:02.719
<i>Should I have stopped her?</i>

00:21:03.428 --> 00:21:06.223
<i>No. I could not.</i>

00:21:06.306 --> 00:21:09.726
<i>The woman reached
her century's greatest villain status.</i>

00:21:10.602 --> 00:21:12.020
<i>I could never destroy it.</i>

00:21:13.313 --> 00:21:16.233
<i>Nor could I look away.</i>

00:21:55.147 --> 00:21:58.942
<i>That was the last time I saw Loulan.</i>

00:22:07.951 --> 00:22:09.619
{\an8}<i>My body feels heavy.</i>

00:22:09.703 --> 00:22:12.956
{\an8}<i>Come to think of it,
I have not properly slept in days.</i>

00:22:13.915 --> 00:22:15.083
{\an8}Where is that girl?

00:22:15.167 --> 00:22:16.418
{\an8}She is safe.

00:22:16.501 --> 00:22:18.795
{\an8}More importantly,
you should rest a little.

00:22:19.379 --> 00:22:20.505
Where is she?

00:22:22.382 --> 00:22:23.884
It is best not to get too close.

00:22:30.182 --> 00:22:33.268
{\an8}They are the children of the Shi clan,
those who died.

00:22:33.351 --> 00:22:35.937
{\an8}Why are they sleeping here?

00:22:36.021 --> 00:22:39.483
{\an8}She insisted.
Once she did, none of us could say no.

00:22:40.692 --> 00:22:43.487
{\an8}Terrible. She looks terrible.

00:22:44.071 --> 00:22:45.739
{\an8}So do you.

00:22:48.033 --> 00:22:50.243
<i>I knew that if I came back
with a wound on my face,</i>

00:22:50.327 --> 00:22:52.496
<i>my subordinates would be punished.</i>

00:22:53.288 --> 00:22:57.000
{\an8}<i>And yet, I still granted Loulan’s request.</i>

00:22:57.084 --> 00:22:59.127
{\an8}It doesn't matter what happens to me.

00:22:59.211 --> 00:23:03.048
{\an8}Still. It was for the best
that the General was not here to see this.

00:23:03.548 --> 00:23:05.634
Yes, very much so.

00:23:06.468 --> 00:23:07.511
{\an8}Wait outside.

00:23:15.227 --> 00:23:17.104
{\an8}If I had not been here,

00:23:17.187 --> 00:23:18.438
{\an8}she wouldn't have ended up like this.

00:23:28.073 --> 00:23:30.534
What exactly are you doing,

00:23:31.159 --> 00:23:32.285
Lord Jinshi?

00:23:44.131 --> 00:23:45.090
I...

00:23:46.091 --> 00:23:48.552
PREVIEW OF THE NEXT EPISODE

00:23:57.811 --> 00:24:00.230
{\an8}<i>The next episode is "The Beginning."</i>

00:24:00.313 --> 00:24:00.939
MAOMAO
SHISUI

00:24:01.022 --> 00:24:01.982
Subtitle translation by:
Abhishek Chand Ramola

